<h2>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Foundations Class</h2>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;The foundations class is basically just to show you the basics of coding and to get you started. In this class you learn the basics of html and css. You make webpages and eventually make a website.</p>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;It's a good class to be in as a beginner.</p>
