<h2>Foundations Class Curriculum</h2>

<table>
  <tr>
    <th>Week</th>
    <th>Subject</th>
    <th>Description</th>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Week 1</td>
    <td>HTML Basics</td>
    <td>This week you will learn the basics of HTML and learn about what you will be focusing on</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Week 2</td>
    <td>Website Layout</td>
    <td>This week you will design what your first webpage will look like</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Week 3</td>
    <td>Start Using Computer</td>
    <td>This week you will either get a computer or use one you already have</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Week 4</td>
    <td>Color & Images</td>
    <td>This week you will learn how to add Color and Images to a webpage</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Week 5</td>
    <td>About Me</td>
    <td>This week you will work on making your About Me webpage</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Week 6</td>
    <td>Adding Links & Videos</td>
    <td>This week you will learn how to add links and videos to your webpage</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Week 7</td>
    <td>Making Tables & Lists </td>
    <td>This week you will learn how to add tables and lists to your webpage</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Week 8</td>
    <td>Inputs</td>
    <td>This week you will learn how to add date, radio, and checkbox inputs</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Week 9</td>
    <td>CSS</td>
    <td>This week you will learn about the basics of CSS/td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Week 10</td>
    <td>CSS Webpage</td>
    <td>This week you will make a CSS webpage with what we learned</td>
  </tr>
</table>

.
</body>
</html>
